idget</li><li>Live chat record storage</li><li>Chat surveys and polls</li><li>Draggable chat box</li><li>Integration with Google Analytics</li><li>User anonymity</li><li>Missed live chat notification</li><li>Compatibility with translation plugins for multilingual support</li><li>Typing insights and preset answers</li><li>Live chat widget appearance on specific pages</li><li>3CX integration for multichannel communications, including audio and voice chats</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Best </strong><strong>free WordPress live chat plugin</strong><strong> for: </strong>Businesses that lack their own reliable servers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-live-chat-support/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Download 3CX Live Chat</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>12. Click to Chat</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-11-1024x576.png\" alt=\"wordpress chat plugins click to chat \" class=\"wp-image-614694\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-11-1024x576.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-11-300x169.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-11-768x432.png 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-11-1536x864.png 1536w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-11.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/click-to-chat-for-whatsapp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Click to Chat</a> is an efficient and free chat plugin that lets you and your audience communicate directly on WhatsApp in a single click.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With Click to Chat, visitors can find answers to their questions by contacting your WhatsApp account, WhatsApp business account, or group chat.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of Click to Chat</strong>:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Lightweight chat widget</li><li>Animations&nbsp;</li><li>Pre-filled messages</li><li>Well-defined shortcodes</li><li>Integration with e-commerce platforms like WooCommerce</li><li>Nine styles, including image addition</li><li>Hide chat widget option based on factors such as device, post ID, category, and post type&nbsp;</li><li>Integration with Google Analytics, Facebook pixel, and Google Ads</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Best </strong><strong>free WordPress live chat plugin</strong><strong> for: </strong>Businesses that use WhatsApp.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/click-to-chat-for-whatsapp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Download Click to Chat</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>13. REVE Chat</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-12-1024x576.png\" alt=\"wordpress chat plugins reve live chat plugin\" class=\"wp-image-614695\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-12-1024x576.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-12-300x169.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-12-768x432.png 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-12-1536x864.png 1536w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-12.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.revechat.com/signup\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">REVE Chat</a> is a free cloud-based WordPress live chat plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>REVE Chat provides a single platform that empowers you to manage communications with your customers in real-time on different channels, including audio or video chats, and on social networks like Viber and Facebook Messenger.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of REVE Chat:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Intuitive and customizable chat window</li><li>Auto trigger option</li><li>Screen-sharing</li><li>Real-time website visitor analytics</li><li>Co-browsing with live chat and WordPress</li><li>Customer query department management&nbsp;</li><li>Chat monitoring&nbsp;</li><li>Supports over 20 different languages</li><li>Integration with WordPress and social media platforms</li><li>24/7 support on any weekday</li><li>Mobile application available</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Best </strong><strong>free WordPress live chat plugin</strong><strong> for: </strong>Businesses that use several different communication channels.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/revechat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Download REVE Chat</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>14. Chaty</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-13-1024x576.png\" alt=\"wordpress chat plugins chaty\" class=\"wp-image-614696\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-13-1024x576.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-13-300x169.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-13-768x432.png 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-13-1536x864.png 1536w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-13.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/chaty/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Chaty</a> is an omnichannel free live chat WordPress plugin that empowers you to interact with your customers on different communication channels. It supports up to 19 different platforms, including Instagram, SMS, Facebook, and Twitter.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With Chaty, you can communicate with your audience on their favorite chat platforms, and your customers can easily contact you after they exit your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of Chaty:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Easy chat window customization</li><li>Drag-and-drop interface</li><li>Date scheduling</li><li>Availability display</li><li>Trigger and targeting options</li><li>Attention effects</li><li>Pending messages icon</li><li>Custom channel button option</li><li>WhatsApp chat popup</li><li>Integration with Google Analytics, all WordPress themes, and e-commerce websites</li><li>Integration with popular page builders, including Divi, Elementor, Beaver, and WooCommerce</li><li>Mobile optimization</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Best </strong><strong>free WordPress live chat plugin</strong><strong> for: </strong>Businesses that use several different communication channels (runner-up).</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/chaty/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Download Chaty</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>15. Userlike</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-14-1024x576.png\" alt=\"wordpress chat plugins userlike live chat\" class=\"wp-image-614697\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-14-1024x576.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-14-300x169.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-14-768x432.png 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-14-1536x864.png 1536w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-14.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.userlike.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Userlike</a> is another free plugin that lets you chat with your customers through popular channels, such as SMS, Facebook Messenger, and WhatsApp.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Userlike enables continuous chats with website visitors as they move through different pages by keeping the chat box on the screen.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of Userlike:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Customizable live chat window</li><li>Automated responses</li><li>Operator groups and registration forms</li><li>Proactive chat invitations</li><li>Multiple chats</li><li>Intuitive native chatbot (Chat Butler)</li><li>Automatic translator for seven languages</li><li>Offline messages</li><li>Service time and rating settings</li><li>Real-time visitor and event analytics</li><li>Integration with chat analytics, social networks, and other apps, including Slack, Facebook Messenger, Asana, Pipedrive, Telegram, and Help Scout</li><li>Optimized for mobile</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Best </strong><strong>free WordPress live chat plugin</strong><strong> for:</strong> Businesses that use apps like Slack or Asana.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a class=\"rank-math-link\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/userlike/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Download Userlike</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>16. Chatra Live Chat</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-15-1024x576.png\" alt=\"wordpress chat plugins chatra live chat chatbot plugin\" class=\"wp-image-614698\" srcset=\"//oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-15-1024x576.png 1024w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-15-300x169.png 300w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-15-768x432.png 768w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-15-1536x864.png 1536w, //oceanwp.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image-15.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/chatra-live-chat/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Chatra Live Chat</a> is a free WordPress live chat plugin that provides a trustworthy environment to convert your website guests to customers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Chatra Live Chat saves your cart and increases your sales by empowering you to contact visitors on the checkout page proactively. This gives you a chance to guide your customers and attend to their concerns and questions.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Key Features of Chatra Live Chat</strong>:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Simple interface</li><li>Unlimited concurrent conversations</li><li>Offline messages and group chats</li><li>Typing insights and typo corrections</li><li>Agent photos available